  "method": [
    "Take a large pot and heat oil over the medium heat.",
    "Put garlic cloves and onion in it and cook for 6-8 minutes.",
    "Put cumin.",
    "Add black beans, frozen corn, and tomatoes. Stir constantly.",
    "Add green chile sauce, chicken broth, and white rice in it and bring it",
    "to boil.",
    "Lower the heat and cook while keeping it covered.",
    "Stir constantly. When rice is tender, add mozzarella in it. Cook until it",
    "is melted.",
    "Add salt and put avocado, hot sauce, tortilla chips, and sour cream on",
    "the top."
